text: Usage usage: pcommit <package-file> ... This command is used to install a package in the system. This command should only be used by system administrators with authority to maintain the MediationZone software. For further information, see the https://infozone.atlassian.net/wiki/x/hVv9F . Return Codes Listed below are the different return codes for the pcommit command: Code Description Code Description 0 Will be returned if the argument count is incorrect, or if the command is successful. 3 Will be returned if the package you want to commit does not exist. 4 Will be returned if the user name and password is missing. 5 Will be returned if the commit failed. 6 Will be returned if any uncaught failures occur during commit.
